{"tid":1386412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線中國組：香港反修例的內地民眾視角","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:00:36.000Z","uid":278587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"310deca1b34d181d55bdb5c6af41ba806f8ffc6a","tid":1386412,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/856265858071988/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F856265858071988%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=15bf6973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/856265858071988/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港修例風波，由六月到現在已經一個多月，不少國際媒體都有大篇幅報道，內地民眾對這場運動有多少認識，又有甚麼看法呢？<br />\n<br />\n有人一提起就直斥有份參與的大學生為「暴徒」，又有人直指示威者「很野蠻」。<br />\n<br />\n如果想在內地看到香港的情況，又可以看到些甚麼剩下來民眾可以看到的就只有官方報道，和網上流傳的片段，好像一條機場集會圍堵老人家的片，近日就在抖音和不同微信群傳來傳去。<br />\n<br />\n而在微信上，都有部分自媒體關注香港情況，他們形容香港是暴亂，是港獨分子在禍亂香港，甚至讚揚元朗白衣人打得好，更有人在微博上，發起要去香港保衛元朗。<br />\n<br />\n但另一邊廂，有內地維權人士就因為在Facebook和Twitter，轉發香港情況，並寫上形勢大好和加油的字眼，而被指尋釁滋事，被行政拘留15日。"},{"pid":"f289559e7ee367f4f18ad3d11f93903a0269d4c5","tid":1386412,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"知都唔講得真話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋知咁多盞自尋煩惱 知少啲生活會幸福啲"},{"pid":"fcd8499b7089ec5362e5cb8eb4586f5428a2e4a5","tid":1386412,"uid":7076,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e36iqQ5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe36iqQ5.gif&h=efa388e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdbf62935567029478de5c62f13dd31caec383e","tid":1386412,"uid":2292